rder-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;反应很快。&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BwfeAvqWClR80j7xzCl_e14yzrHrCw6LEM5PPLR92Bt87p3ZlQGntfq_8b4HH-uLy8D9eG1GnFFRpqbKfnO5gras50kFBuUKnKty5mxlj1n2bH8TPGpGXIiZ-mMqdAezV7-rN5kPQGwFRzFBMOpRO39zV14EWPMe0y1KjwPxlN5hcg9gFA_yaWSZHys3voMm66MyLVNWbpqYc8_DgVwKlwGdim7PSxNQ5dIf0E0uzsMhgB-fhu9zHQEwJ_KGCoBUX9AaZhv4jR3M6NJCHMECd1J2jncWksfmmkYrvT3-AyrCe6g58fkbP2XcJ9J2zYM1FfiUKsjENoDk_R6p9F7gGbTcqAAO9CqnxyMUIZq1Q3v_qUKOaH4evjA2fO8/qe8VBFRjE5lvJPDXkz9pczKU1FN5V1OL/7" target="_blank"&gt;欧盟誓言要进行报复&lt;/a&gt;，而中国为全球供应链和经济增长都&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iy7jz4dXKMlTf2TrvR8sqh2V0DHkitYfKvPe-wteLvOzBBSjganT1r7MouTL8SNW3ZActVsR8ZA2ScsoAbWKvPiYy_l9Sa20C3LpWL-1ysDjTinXA--RIFh53vywlec4CugGqt2dxoilNltNz_6c2ZG3R4p14EQeuJDoyFU7OG2ZbYojUtna1oOSVO-UAxH2ZgBHX0tu9jGc-VxgEcPXPJKJ3QHGZVIlI_S-LBnZVNk92XfzM_JSM58DGYV5qYqerb_Q_98glq9HEZGCSbhS9Bm1mPQ_8wyNHa3K0u-ryou4AmIKNT5wqwEeI1SRGIRZim9sQLZgVVU47WJ3IJT277-FUCMaNoltVFxAr539YUuvBUuXS-3-6AJtvXc/fecVNsIJAdbg1OvILD35l-TtyW-zh-Fl/7" target="_blank"&gt;构成了义务&lt;/a&gt;。至于财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent），他向美国的贸易伙伴&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/r7cGYwNhnxeD_bfR4gSpB_lSR1S-io_NhRJl4OtaCJOpCfAofXn2CdLzdunJwyVSYrpybxVYTpLBFTjy9dXVaJmxhvS7dfH2AONNQYlkFe_eE26aJNdCbDRgxs_UtJ73lLl2btAQC0QJ5oED-cM1orgG_s8s5Tt2tz4ytdUCS7Icef0jOmeSVUjK40MxIju-TWT61H8sdZRQ68ugzLA9rDUEbBNr9tpzyQaiuibzsh5PzQS2wcMD-TEvr5CR4CiGVTqgdEaTI99sSgPk6wLiJNsaFvF2N1BEdfWeczTUrip2maN5yOpGON1t0U8NC9aFNHaZ-XJ8a_6uw-IFe5wmNq99FDZJAGCbPfx3kRaloUM_7KrsHYnmL6orqCU/3lyG3fKxgBdjWpw6yqGsQZFx6qQg9TRA/7" target="_blank"&gt;提供了这一建议&lt;/a&gt;：“只要您不进行报复，这就是这个数字的高端。”同时，一系列关税使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dkhLg2vVa3PUO_Wek1cV_-o5RAel2A4QuqQIDR1cIG9UUVV_PKYXen_6oXr1suxV7Lc1f4OENSIH9iFU0bCogs3hKwFESBqGJnHiQqOMGjRLGjCTla_On7OZX5jy7zpDQXyRXefvpiP4Q7_Zl1z3HZ9DmleISuOSxpLDgr-HcqqDCoXGFuSfncr4H2niVVvTpBBYEIP83Ys25VtOOYjP9Djpg0wBwO2SHmD_IfGCavndL2o3MqEIP7hGzFnXpHC6am-X1BdOfFmHhLFrNctUgbwlfpdbfgBZmUq8NCKFtjYA1vPt7s10UvqudPzk9NPhGCK3OR-n2rhec8vT179PCfkD3A0wYwPBbJYcjgrIyXHT6Sb3gDot9hhiQVs/0OwYV6AnkCu4x3ZvZLbD4wwCor-2k1oQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;美联储陷入了艰难的位置，&lt;/a&gt;因为它与增长和通货膨胀有关。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;全球金融市场&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DU9czY3Q8WIxH5STgE8oAK9TDbfFnbATMGTQbMb9rkakk5DHG7U5dfPUiT3xzDTVwcsxtmllRURKBxyplivU_ub-zBjazEYFSj5FmowcMR_sQo52m4Jcp6jusTtdhuGFt2HdVeFpGJaOwb8HkXXyDwAtXfTD04WH28SDqaQ-ywBYwmk6Ekux70_cPKL0l_B0TzzTdQ3S2hQKJxd_N3PM5ax6WpX0TdsWDeQbZAWzRKviuYI-cqZSjsQspgIlpejF7cP0DhiVw6X3NK59BKGhQgAFUZUjhSfoV5-uaHuffw3GjlH4qMTzpmO8pmvhhetxA5z7EtxH8eV_vrb3u7kBaHFPCBsz4cYRQAe4xOSqYBFNKLPV490C-pd8VUk/sI98iBdsUSmOD3Z_1XS5922O0VxB_-c1/7" target="_blank"&gt;也做出了巨大的反应&lt;/a&gt;，而美国的期货却陷入了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yzg06M9vXA-loQBgS87FUXHVEjrydUdT7CZC1qATbn1wilpDXnoHVRglR6SjCABiJAU4KvtzkrFKgAhUxMdM3Stbs381snnHeYatdccadnYGyhwBgxEfkSUZuBNvdsUBaVjce4TJHsjrV7L94IjZRXd7E_wKLwVFr_4U4LSedsMG95PqOaK9_Y-QiG0-2yPsWASeqI3i7_n4N_vqRJMHle782yDGc3U82t5moCFVIBNb6H5TPz8rzpbq61qblWaLkMFEEbP1sNJfI3eRJALpvmXrLW7LSc_mN2OTYNz8iYIbdgiTrJVQc24T8OW_68oxVZ_dMJ1ifKZwGq58o-h2QICX9e1fab7KHrBJtlFFEH3KT6DMRTedHmifZ4M/14YfjbUk99HCqzqUMR4c7W5sYlM6JksA/7" target="_blank"&gt;全面的贸易战&lt;/a&gt;可能使美国经济陷入经济衰退的担忧。避风港的资产再次以黄金跳来跳去，取得了纪录。由于这一切都可以，这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2aQbU6gv7qygks8iHMjGj_sJAr1ZiViEQvIyk5LNfJ-8LgaKlhrVlTTwOVxRYDXeR2sOUmRM-X9BA1w5XVwlS7hpk9k-_j3R1oM0MKu6k3kFcF4pkzK7P1GWNB4wvvZATXPFjMV5sAnBSQqHMDcE7TcZet8vYarIsaMv2bcnjK1mWp7gCVU-GzGh4B7hvhtpNvBc_JtWjcMgE5sZkOffEQbj23hrvS8y5SZPJYl9dEfFzdYrErybyh53pV4o_YzblNiRLFNH4dBo1DWFW_36cnudEVTXHTdr-WhrevYvuAiIoqUMxOoXh3qX_eyiKjkVFEYxL7nsXGPdhFpczfXq7f_b92au3z3bh_Pzri6mKiHh4G7sqNvic6jo_wA/xuEa3tAHb9UrHUIvaF9x8YpGVsh5R_Z_/7" target="_blank"&gt;战略家和投资者对贸易措施的看法&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;贸易战争&lt;/strong&gt;，关税威胁和物流冲击正在振奋企业并传播波动。通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WiuPafAwyvDPns4Vq1LLnXb8MTlPcONGlKAZnftnycv5uf7zt93Ye6Ti8XM2FsTWyfaGMZ_eaXxYvbgWDI7dWFg62bZ4QI8Ye4y5Y4LLOeSX5DDgFfqGWGuwBdHVCE7Z5DzfZBlyaG1qbV61QKsS9j-8WTpC5YbsU0Wct6uZEm1HPs8gohkmL29u91fVW2FcxpFHaoRP8R-Ujn208sZnSfhEpcvxuD0Y8lxcvk-nGxPWUSrhbtjGxGUU5pHTEHWQbOYpGfV4Gg2Ft9HajgbO0TRPZgQbk3RrZmPYrajeUxIb_UZfTRVVIhOA85-0QinNCJ2kqhTTuWoHEeeVVQ9QRKoXSaJftDFZatpI5w2aq7ohiLE_Vdr8KVnRs0c/myHhkbOeYSoUG56bsvwhCAWh_fifv99D/7"&gt;新闻通讯&lt;/a&gt;了解全球商务的新秩序。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;参议院共和党人&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;也从DC发出消息&lt;/strong&gt;，推出了预算蓝图，旨在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/klVUVkMpeULUoxNsEKNfY2IUT9RNcq_DewTawWwa91sf7A8MefL8AbTcPA8bFmslURXvSKA95qZwf7SRcTqIDUeby31Tw3AelSlBTCZJsccDEvIHt3qS_TIrvO6A_yT2JDOOwY-fU6ir4CSfcg1yx9WWRjMxI543c9iO-xxBOqZfQoJ2JroO93hXOveLoHzEOMlFvex31g3RuT62SZlTOMer8Lo6IvKqMeOgQHRoSjPlw0Ol7Ccdsivp0JC8qk42Y5IPJAF0yQJcATUF7PMe9PAIQGnnHRlIar0mt4PG3IlrMyrRBTRysjukVeuXX4Wc1yVjBtI2R0rVUgVMO7yw3ZpCcTrQxTB2XNaPF5VPU7An-P0a43RJ05MWvvI/cffxlP2Hmd7uaUxiKli7tjWjAhWpvd1U/7" target="_blank"&gt;快速续签特朗普的减税措施&lt;/a&gt;，并在本周对该决议的计划投票之前，对国家的借贷限额提高。 Bessent表示，联邦政府有可能按时&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/08bNhRlSnTt8X-23HCwAvdGWZ-lbiYBGJVQKdLyDsImeFnmtHepujDMOg6a7Fmaxb4f5ds8rCsyPrNH5MPM3AD_eF1DaAs6fblVwrpykMMNzCepPeY5iEizy2rkVAcupRukIiLZkSCeyFUdsPTuwDon945B9EhydaNMsMuxN-apUNBSozpOW9HxnMn5PRRTfoOUV8bWyGpiI8fawSs5YGJBBDJ4VAq6gIFC6Ut9yT5e9q2PH1pZ27H3AQGFUEY_KYL2Bd9CiSVpeSJcNrmwSaXMfU5BRw5sAB