" target="_blank"&gt;100亿美元的天然气&lt;/a&gt;数据中心。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在这个关头，&lt;/strong&gt;值得提醒自己，AI繁荣如何创造&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DBswuTEp2oen_T0IGfhLQ5Fa_zCVty_1uABqyJcb_4-1i8aO_MSAV61ily-qRGPT7qb6MKPJZ1IkqCzb9cpbXPZZFbzRYxXCiUinUCkGi_W_0_bnYQLKCGsxW-P4P4Uxt9PUR9AXcJDOBhvtpqhRTZm_o8__QsAdLTkhS_o2x-9QZFpgjQL_lcu7tU_eKVKGtDE9cDr3JWrpQRMSr2qBe1UvwzR97R6rDos128lCE4K9EC-a1U-h-zGmLbsCEWRZQOXS0BRkJjk4unUk895M7GSLB0JPSpbWZoQxLajsJe6D1wCtqNIIGq8hemZwz8eOkwC5F8R76z4n1bBRkO9jzhWvYgTsoZwDSzoxkMpghS6wRMtw_Oo73mEJqmE/08ZQNV-fv5HzN7IMyTvhkpIjdx00_4PE/7" target="_blank"&gt;历史上最有价值的垄断。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wgwJgF3CAbERsX2GXpUKdoi17grHcrTSGptsUepNAzCWUsDUOOSQjd73TcSBhrh9hzCvLEKTWBQfCKCPW7sIRNWLWcZzA2zao263h0NLLyKi8Zi-Ij-qqZip4nYU0DdwsTrMJlV3VlZpPfNL--XFvYNQJe5eHBdPWJEQgcEOz98tknn2wFJ1V0atKM7te6eAUXaiqMY0oRETAyvO28Izxi8QoCTL1jLMI8mseUIiftpnTMWIv0LHjbnea1YRI4rZUmDD-4qPTOxc52B3F_jyQcYPGqnwmueRViB8uGHeUGSUnsRruG8gNyAufNlKJ5GCeSfCHayWLasnKqw1dvUyEBd__QQT6L2zA2TR-Ee5-QZ2IlPsfeqSMYDDwDk/_QDBKLQpj9sXtmITjPjHVLm4ouYKnWGT/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixLUp0Xz7h1s/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixLUp0Xz7h1s/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpad