href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vmTg9D2zwVg74gTbHkNETQbvunfhGjTI-HW6PNX8N3C0BIt7mDGXi5Gxa5TGZ9nFIcr4sYGYBoGJ9wC-CVC3DQ6O5-3AcpCtM5SernM2uaz8A1hpjMC25h0CAFeNlUHZgS7MgnO47Sa5nMZvXZtZKFAkTuStv2Dl9G6el3HC_mgNAEeZDOgsiNMa4ewl7BGv1qPnYjR--85kr0nb9vFBTn1HpyP2XsXGCcVyXcXisBmhB5ygoVFWRLBWVPrh4gHUYQPkIbMfRCmDhygvqLSmlIMcuFxhEj2aZnmp0XfSZNnUPM3cwWexBamM6_5ismzy5up3CWl5UEJ36OUg3y95QMIxWi8xg3QnEUZIPnfp1vUfN2_bZ22ul1ockNg/jhMArKswpwfHxxOI_Qg1SZyXWD5E3X-V/7" target="_blank"&gt;那么所有这些都会实现&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;成千上万的英国企业在雇主的税收和工资增加之前&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/obRSDTB292Ygpj4urlf8vj7F2qZA_iRZCpdBEHoWyd6VmFwsLLSrVOdBbWA8bk5qMaXCQlK20dQApZ5KdrwXrgB8ymGLZh1XungZAdaXiVanJcjtopfX2sF1ge78nqjpqTlL1GOlBkslLiNd4eA6-Lv_Mx6tO-xbpnHl6obFqIRmRaAcW4HtpCsqwxruer0-lvLmC1GckiPL0MiauUt9AFh-ligXtPnJM_qWrFnrHOi11PEPPrLRU2SA0rgK3aUqgzfo6WaujZB9ztEEzWkJ4GQ5nV41M2Ck2geIcILIZ2t2EwySWBpFsR6sd9ymQ-EHanDzo52bVykGj-B7M1yojgI5tdzwukYomMZQHvihORXqGn292aV5SyAng2o/N97y55xDsAJfWcE9CJ7Dd0KxA1IvI2-o/7" target="_blank"&gt;申请破产&lt;/a&gt;。同时，较高的税收和账单将使典型的英国家庭在未来的财政年度&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sY37pDxScu0NUjaXSRgbmG6PT6rLb1kjLI_8SuP9Qw1yc_MuVkNsaNDYKd-QHCbrej2WFosuJiT-MZw5zKSeqyjLbMrwkkjzK0-qaAKSLun3RS9I86stnU-nRMCMOfH46DGDhE5ywnZa6DWT9_C0rKW0DCDRGmBWwwDmn2r0z8KEeblE0spTqfo1BybHYoaveEU3HFf2HJCzy8hIulabXktU3dC9NVKglxUtGPwizmkHB29IdHSCbEW5a-CJAi5dJVhWnXEg-PIPkcvWGjI_7C-ODkWtyqPzcW6zn4Evg_VmYT0PokCduaWrn1bV6ggSkeEEisCBTWs6_xGTGoG7MzvR4KFMecUik-iIiwipNHC1tL3c_HpU8bcAP44/nDxHliJem9DFkpCri9PDoWxQCWttIAcK/7" target="_blank"&gt;较差400英镑&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;土耳其的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ouBhbMJQhWikF-XOXDNi9Hs7B2TKzuTxx1lQZV-idusFLlMne8zHqyo-p8EQjSiZVIpaRDLfFJLL-3nCMg7gIxFnTYfB8jS3G7cKJZ3uqdVxbPPHufeJYGgjHMfYex2dOpIGrCtTZHo__SsDhlM9jUkp7ywHyleaTJcpTtq4_jwJ5NgRvvPbhKJv5T-epT1fFYe6o49kwqN7uzdhkAa-ONWVix8p6F0G1jxPTsfOUz5sSfmLsnyDUNXOpYOZTyMzSGeSig89opkvc