lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-QkYB3BKfzg9Fr4XDrlmKcH5PxLuKhcLwUmesSTVC2FJVcA9i9RSYUAd0GncvqCOWVJMTbnt6zN2dz5_2wWHQWjjKgzgxPWhVFmAf5VS2eFjyQs5vcvnUmrBxHwu1UfbYPkIknkxTpwY64r6N3g4Svw89fRLDmLHygCioCpX1X3ZFXyxk_Yc8DG8DC2h6qSpR01yiFGErRWSJigKcIflnc3lq9GzeaQ3ZcuZLYtD0ZFJ_jBXNAeCQFIU4UHDe3yOIPfp41hfomWEzdl1e5h0Ws2Bdc0ZOIZUNvbbsZxulmN4gHBjn4f3OUOzpYHu0pZA1pVA9I4_qxzSG2aSbScJ9hbxQi2S89yC7IkE6sH2toxzY1OxrnKUu3npxX8/CyeBvvPWzNuGtnZs8bWuR-kdMpbANMS-/7" target="_blank"&gt;Vontier Corp.&lt;/a&gt;的首席执行官Mark Morelli表示，暂停了一项政府计划资助新的充电站，可能意味着美国至少将拥有200,000个高速充电器。这是预期约40万的一半。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-mAZ5ymbii1sZZ1UNDxkN8Fe6thJJphkdgZ647mjuf3DFcBrZIgy6HYR-JblK8DOHmTLS7BTFEMQpWesinjdaoEZg7N6GGMe_bghrVnbqv9hI_swNVH8xP8hmvc0ofuc2kMHs3wY33WvbyCscBPLLrUnncwyOKTnJyVuW45f_Qxe8ILhxFJ1T-3B-jyJKa1-RcYjuNdUe1G3CTIgFlX73iFt61mfMG9FVnLFMid-MH0mSj-5pAYiMdwQSgZ6h1bgNmck6rupyckXxxJKcFDYa3zvbd2BS3DPDcm2OUnBlb4jlUqIrLDQKwC_cZ08XKrpXHwXx5BMDALYv9ShYkj8GHJpr1SgO5hzgWPb3Ht3xYwZ1kN0O29W-9O8UPM/NMqs7gqLCzTwoDzq1hrNTuUnkn3cDM1Y/7" target="_blank"&gt;美国运输部&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/105cUJOSPlIp1IeTKIbY-h1WjCBsCmGVSNtts6aePLiZDm2jQYheNEoDnij8OaPys7SvvaFbkdELtdcrWHVCEc2dlvr_EB_zjuTs3lNYHOEdozvdS_nuHdYbBDiJcQ6FCVGVmr2NkiJJU8FUHZaTqmgk0q4fDKcdILN5gCrkct9RURkoC82BksA06R3woaf8bTH5AJnyEGZJQDV0AgHO5q-ancMh7iF0ffqUtw9GcIcbmVxTZ-bu7QKikuuJoUoX88Zd6D3y5SmlJ1EsDOlVrADX23Q_5ZFiHcL3qr9OGNHwa1y-ez8_ReOdCDULKfDUByiqpSvDW-R_EoVhcE-IZAlIPgpWDcTsKMhDP5FYNZvqDWptnjScLJuioK4/HQjpCixoqU7afQhCWPERNsNT5stKpP8w/7" target="_blank"&gt;联邦公路管理局&lt;/a&gt;表示， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Uh26XkM5uEt1EXwizelXkFX29BOxoY2MlpIzHwZubPji6RQoCSrTN7fykItRjQAHYlJ5ZhOUfMdrYgEOZ2lZLhmhPuBc_8ZF-ApClgbtsSpdNWGubCXYCb8nJb-igEqU9sxPxWJwQOxZdLwiscj6lew6T6j230ZvN2WU4-gIm1qLJIxkjxuIzaPgjIJ4Q_F5PVWClpdExf64TeP