om成为最新的大牌，涉足竞争，向白宫提交了一旦价值600亿美元的企业购买。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1pR0uDek2RUqbA7Vy994AEf9RyCDs7rVROHOJagDPfRfSW_3YS_HvcgnvhWylBe6rVYFahB78I_Lccmr4q-hOUR4CuYFSiNS2Vl3zppi8Knh9drIjOf8DwYv4VgtlLeS4BWFo-7X2JH3E8CyRv8ixR5XLnqGd1K9KNfe_-fssMUvkTs-q11hmbBGhG-R-QshoFX7tmUKJQ_epLI69xAxbyyhf2yyyULLtgt2ITfhy_0UW4AdiHjQXYZ4M9mXreWfs6QL5YTT3leLyqTqaEkHBwJE1lao6YCSNpIqFMMb1dJUg8F0gOmtOhEwjaJ_X-RQxMjs_VV6I6jfbrLMGDBe9tumIUsKTJRquBpDS1PQ8WNLFq_ZHeBElvBvoaQ/tWglD0HDBzeGBPvMdc5TyLiLoWsT4mhf/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;《特朗普&lt;/a&gt;：特朗普：主持人斯蒂芬妮·佛兰德斯》的最新一集中，《金融时报》首席经济学评论员马丁·沃尔夫（Martin Wolf）也加入了。美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认为，当前的全球贸易体系对美国不公平，关税是平衡规模的工具。但是世界如何到达这一点？在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EiVJNXk71XQMGipoZSb5lX1RhAO6CqncjeT345pn-aqPqBunnOZrkUX96oETjJgnlhurJhmGGCMSl14f_CnKpw4NyLnhjq-dsUv56qaQ0uw5dOVA29VPejYbIkGmeFnusGzujpozvJofc8P2V6LoTTlU8Yo27WDzoezjqqMa5raiB__hwk4p-oqwYyZfHSM--HFwENXf4Q0zO9zSHgPIySIYvn_7UEV5AsXeAj0SlpO45Ue2k4OQpLG1Oq9lmlVkDUOs4m5qxvmmeviaCdz27faT7SUZliaHfFtgFNT0IN6egKC-bgNvihM2BBrwV_A2DW5B0ep-Jlqz243OpR9eiKvDNSUTNklSHeDn7R_h8q3FuWjNtAmTXTLP7tykoIJd-5c_wsUwty_wjs2ehMG2u2T52Wz0qZS89ZGW971Di4Iy0Sk6MZgwBEhpugnjNZxVxdfj2RI0AypnOYpaXpty32ynfBtSp01YJ3kcpBjbfgFQ8DZGR-rBfYGwAYyyP6evRLjvPZTIgNnYn4uM3ZW0Lc6W/4NXGfMD5MInLAurfp2sibeUY2HKIDLGg/7"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; ， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YfR_QekR0eXxnZ4RvAh68K3ZqAcMQsVi1SERwNuvODLeYtIGYSBpwEZcUDS0Y7JeVG1A4HW8P5QG0JQG9wZv56vJNZ5GHcnHK-quO7h-U92lpoygWJ6GtWn6PG6UM2eEBXUKFwoC0vviplbOm2aTRigJKKm_XmT-shk8Lng8QRmgfvMcnqvHvDkinZE1e3HMWhueqy-6V5NPDt-5kVrba0iJLCr-4oislqnifOlqmSaO963hu4RTT8ImmTkDJzpmHc5fvP09_vroTSqVuKbyfT1-Hn3knAXeJ1DRoVkTZpmFFY-YHAAZu_jAtLI9WfzzluwKIPx3-1xOoZL-EeXdDCkdK3i4txbnWCzmKN4--XGUVTFHHHtx4bvHsxQFVr4tkchAlSZ7idR27DwStYxV4iOHIB2E50JgvzvbiMYOC7DEzWJpIsAXhuElFxS896YDtrER3jelh6LI92A_tgpi7ddbRhwo1BtHq8FwrXHQl0wec3oXYGTHixbaUTSCrJylDfP4PAEjMvFSfeT